UASharedPasteboardProgressUI(8)                        System Manager's Manual

NAME
     UASharedPasteboardProgressUI – Progress UI Service for Universal
     Clipboard

DESCRIPTION
     UASharedPasteboardProgressUI is used by useractivityd to display progress
     to the user when a Universal Clipboard transfer is in progress.

